comment._content: Accompanying note: "Griffin Junior High of Tallahassee is one of the competing teams in the State Class CC northern division basketball tournament at the Florida A and M University Gymnasium this weekend. The Griffin squad is, front row, left to right, L. Guidry, L. Kelley, W. Wiggins, J. Smith, E. Lucas; second row, L.C. Gibson, R. Monroe, J. Wright, R. Ribbon, S. Dennis, C. Rambo, W. Holliday."
